Comprehensive Cost-Benefit Model Workbook
=========================================

Worksheets:
1. Executive Dashboard - Overview of key metrics and ROI
2. Cost Analysis - Detailed construction and operational costs
3. Benefit Quantification - Property values, economic activity, health benefits
4. ROI Calculations - Annual returns, payback periods, sensitivity analysis
5. Funding Scenarios - Multiple funding mix scenarios
6. Risk Analysis - Monte Carlo simulation and risk assessment
7. Implementation Timeline - Gantt chart and milestone tracking
8. Municipal Breakdown - Cost-benefit analysis by municipality
9. Sensitivity Testing - Scenario analysis with adjustable parameters
10. Summary Reports - Formatted reports for different audiences

Key Features:
- Interactive financial model with adjustable assumptions
- Scenario comparison tools
- Sensitivity analysis with tornado charts
- Monte Carlo simulation for risk assessment
- Visual dashboards with key performance indicators
- Automated report generation
- Data validation and error checking
- Comprehensive documentation

This file would contain the complete cost-benefit analysis from Section 10.3, allowing users to adjust assumptions, run scenarios, and explore the financial implications of different implementation approaches.